T02TD2405E:29b-1: k'a li marga bh'a ba na n'a ma /
T02TD2405E:29b-3: ka phreng sgom pa'i lam zhes bya ba /
T02TD2405E:29b-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2405E:29b-5: don dam kun rdzob rab gsal ba'i //
T02TD2405E:29b-6: aa sogs bzhin bzu rtsa dgu yi //
T02TD2405E:29b-7: rang byung yi ge rnams kyi ni //
T02TD2405E:29b-9: bdag gi gnas bzhi rtsa lnga dang //
T02TD2405E:29b-10: sum mdo rlung lha 'khor lo nas //
T02TD2405E:29b-11: lte bar 'bar ba'i gtum mo la //
T02TD2405E:29b-12: snying ga sbar ba'i 'khor lo yin //
T02TD2405E:29b-13: steng du brtan pa'i 'khor lo gnas //
T02TD2405E:29b-14: spyi bor chu rlung ljang gu ste //
T02TD2405E:29b-15: de rnams la ni rim pa bzhin //
T02TD2405E:29b-16: ka phreng yi ge lnga la dgod //
T02TD2405E:29b-17: thog mar chags pa'i 'dab ma la //
T02TD2405E:29b-18: shar du kam dang lho ru kham //
T02TD2405E:29b-19: nub tu gam ste byang du gham //
T02TD2405E:29b-20: dbus kyi nam mkhar ngam zhes brjod //
T02TD2405E:29b-21: rim bzhin sngo dang dmar dang dkar //
T02TD2405E:29b-22: ser dang sngo ba bsam par bya //
T02TD2405E:29b-23: chags pa skyes te chags pa na //
T02TD2405E:29b-24: chags pa'i nad rnams sel bar byed //
T02TD2405E:29b-25: kam gi rung ni me la phog / gtum mo 'od zer rjes dran nas //
T02TD2405E:29b-26: chu bskams sa brtol rlangs pa byung //
T02TD2405E:29b-27: de nas lte ba nas hi ga h'um bgrang //
T02TD2405E:29b-28: bde chen ha la sems gtad nas //
T02TD2405E:29b-29: bdud rtsi rgyun ni 'bab par bsam //
T02TD2405E:29b-30: lte ba'i rdzing bu bkang byas nas //
T02TD2405E:29b-31: spyi bo'i tshangs bug sgra skad 'byung //
T02TD2405E:29b-32: bde chen khang stong bsam byas nas //
T02TD2405E:29b-33: lte dbus khong stong sems gtad bya //
T02TD2405E:29b-35: rnal 'byor dha ma dhu ma yis //
T02TD2405E:29b-36: de ltar spyang ba'i 'pho ba smras //
T02TD2405E:29b-37: yul nas yul du 'pho byed na //
T02TD2405E:29b-38: rnal 'byor bdag gi mdun du ni //
T02TD2405E:29b-39: bdud rtsi lnga yi mandala bya //
T02TD2405E:29b-40: tsa na ka yi 'bras bu ste //
T02TD2405E:29b-41: thod pa nag por gzhag par bya //
T02TD2405E:29b-42: kunda lta bu'i h'um nyid bri //
T02TD2405E:29b-43: de bzhin rang gi snying ga ru //
T02TD2405E:29b-44: zla tshes steng du h'um nyid bsgom //
T02TD2405E:29b-45: sems nyid rtogs nas rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD2405E:29b-46: thod pa'i dbus su sems gtad nas //
T02TD2405E:30a-2: sems la sems nyid thim par bya //
T02TD2405E:30a-3: de nas me khyer ro blangs la //
T02TD2405E:30a-4: de yi snying gar h'um bsam bya //
T02TD2405E:30a-5: ro langs grub rtags byung ba yis //
T02TD2405E:30a-6: rigs bzang gzhon nu'i rol ni //
T02TD2405E:30a-7: kha sbyor de nyid h'um nyid bsgom //
T02TD2405E:30a-10: seng ge rnam rgyal me tog 'dzin //
T02TD2405E:30a-11: phyag rgya bcas la tshangs pa phye //
T02TD2405E:30a-12: sems nyid ri rab rtse mo'i steng //
T02TD2405E:30a-13: pad 'dab brgyad pa'i ge sar la //
T02TD2405E:30a-14: h'um las sems nyad gtad par bya //
T02TD2405E:30a-15: dpal ldan nag po'i 'pho ba ni //
T02TD2405E:30a-16: dha ma dhu ma bdag gis smras //
T02TD2405E:30a-18: nam mkhar thim 'gyur the tshom med //
T02TD2405E:30a-19: ka phreng bsgom pa'i lam zhes bya ba slob dpon dha ma dhu mas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
